## Graceful Degradation

**Provide fallbacks instead of complete failure:**

```typescript
// Good: Fallback experience
async function loadDashboard() {
  try {
    const data = await fetchDashboard();
    setData(data);
  } catch {
    setData(getCachedDashboard() ?? getEmptyDashboard());
    showBanner("Showing cached data. Some features may be limited.");
  }
}

// Good: Feature-level degradation
const [analytics, setAnalytics] = useState<Analytics | null>(null);
useEffect(() => {
  fetchAnalytics().then(setAnalytics).catch(() => {
    setAnalytics(null);  // Hide analytics section, rest of app works
  });
}, []);
```

